snippet.textDisplay: thanks to coke studio for introducing these folk songs in a modern way,I've never heard of but always yearned to listen to these...........that people barely even heard of. These unknown songs,I wanted to explore so bad someday.....that were on the verge of extinction for the lack of exposure to media. Finally my wish came true.....coke studio created a magnificent stage for songs like this. I can't appreciate enough,I feel incredibly lucky that y'all exist❤❤❤❤❤❤now I could get an access to these.I highly suggest audience to hear the original. lots lots lots of love & support from west bengal
